# Certificate & Graduation

## [**1\. Last Form Notification Email**](https://make.wordpress.org/handbook/wordpress-credits-contribution-internship-program/admin-guide/students/certificate-graduation/#1-last-form-notification-email)

When the student complete the [last feedback form](https://learn.wordpress.org/lesson/complete-the-feedback-form/) of the course, the Airtable automation [“Feedback form3 GRADUATE”](https://airtable.com/appIzQKfwTn5dyPVp/wfluUX3TpDDkVadmZ/wac6QlFBjXBZAnHGO) gets triggered:

* It updates the “Status” to “Pending Graduation” in the Airtable “Students” table (this also triggers the automation [“Update status and start/end date”](https://airtable.com/appIzQKfwTn5dyPVp/wflUYImI8OEvVuc4R/wtrU0Ld8b2Ge5TwZS), that changes the status in the “Student Reports” table for that student too).  
* It sends an email to education@wordpressfoundation.org with the subject “Student pending graduation”.  
* The admin team share the next steps as [schedule here](https://airtable.com/appIzQKfwTn5dyPVp/tblAhLTDYnZ3gVf59/viwg4QrpXTGSZmKub?blocks=hide).

## [**2\. Review Student and Approve Certificate**](https://make.wordpress.org/handbook/wordpress-credits-contribution-internship-program/admin-guide/students/certificate-graduation/#2-review-student-and-approve-certificate)

After receiving that email:

* We review that every task in the student’s report table is correctly completed.  
* We consult with their mentor if something is not clear.  
* If everything is ok, we approve their quiz in Sensei so they can get their Certificate following this path:  
  * Go to [Sensei \> Gradings](https://learn.wordpress.org/wp-admin/admin.php?page=sensei_grading)  
  * Insert the name of the course (WordPress Credits) and the name of the lesson (Get your Certificate)  
  * Find the name of the student in the list.  
  * Click on the blue button for that student.  
  * Apply 1 as grading.  
  * Save.

## [**3\. Update Student Status and Notify**](https://make.wordpress.org/handbook/wordpress-credits-contribution-internship-program/admin-guide/students/certificate-graduation/#3-update-student-status-and-notify)

After the previous step:

* Find the student in the [“Students” table](https://airtable.com/appIzQKfwTn5dyPVp/tbla8GZg5x6NY7aWt/viwLOYmC4mmUiW9qc?blocks=hide).  
* Change their status to “Graduate”.  
* The automation [“Certificate notice after graduation”](https://airtable.com/appIzQKfwTn5dyPVp/wflDiVBB5ZeO4ljvv/wacBAb5d0GT45D248) is triggered:  
  * It sends an email to the student and the mentor to let them know the Certificate is ready to download.  
* The automation [“Update status and start/end date”](https://airtable.com/appIzQKfwTn5dyPVp/wflUYImI8OEvVuc4R/wtrU0Ld8b2Ge5TwZS) is triggered:  
  * It changes the status in the “Student Reports” table for that student.
